      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"chance to rediscover myself\" idea just feels like a joke. There's nothing left to rediscover. The person who could actually do things, the person people actually respected... that person is just dead. It feels like i'm just haunted by a ghost of who i used to be.",
